Simple & Transparent

How It Works

From application to decision in minutes — not days.

1
Tenant Applies
They fill out their profile and securely connect their bank account via Plaid in minutes.
2
Score Calculated
Renterly analyzes income, debt-to-income ratio, credit, and rental history in real time.
3
Landlord Decides
Landlords see a verified Renterly Score instead of raw documents — a clear, trusted signal.
4
Continuous Monitoring
Renterly monitors tenant financials monthly. Landlords get alerted to any major changes in income or credit automatically.
Our Mission

Verified Matches for
Landlords and Tenants

Renterly's mission is to redefine rental transparency for landlords, offering a proprietary system that rates tenant readiness and delivers key market insights. We strive to optimize tenant selection for property managers and give applicants a clear view of their rental fit — for smarter leasing decisions and a lesser likelihood of fallout.

The Renterly Score:
Tailored for Tenants

The Renterly score is engineered to replicate Canadian housing affordability rules — giving us exquisitely accurate predictive capabilities. This unique rating system considers financial compatibility, income verification, liability tracking, and qualifying rent-to-income ratios. Trust in a score crafted for clarity and confidence.

Live Monitoring

Screening Doesn't Stop
at Move-In

Renterly continuously monitors tenant cashflows and credit — every month — so you always know who's living in your unit.

📊
Monthly Cashflow Tracking
We pull live bank data every month to verify your tenant's income hasn't changed and they can still afford rent.
📈
Credit Score Alerts
Get notified the moment a tenant's credit score drops below a threshold — before it becomes a missed payment.
🛡️
Debt-to-Income Monitoring
Track whether your tenant has taken on new liabilities that could jeopardize their ability to pay rent on time.
🔔
Instant Risk Alerts
Receive real-time alerts when a tenant's Renterly Score changes significantly, so you're never caught off guard.
📋
Monthly Score Reports
A detailed monthly report for every tenant showing score trend, cashflow health, and any red flags to watch for.
🏦
Plaid-Powered Verification
Bank-grade financial data pulled directly from your tenant's accounts via Plaid — no pay stubs, no guesswork.
